WEBVTT

00:06.120 --> 00:07.950
Alex, get out of bed already!

00:07.980 --> 00:09.740
I don't want to be late for Driver's Ed.

00:09.770 --> 00:10.940
Be right there!

00:11.940 --> 00:13.900
Ready.

00:13.930 --> 00:16.239
I hate it when you flash
in places without warning me.

00:16.270 --> 00:17.780
Why do you do that?

00:17.810 --> 00:21.120
Because in the time it would've
taken me to come down the stairs,

00:21.160 --> 00:23.820
I got dressed, brushed my teeth,
and made this bowl of cereal.

00:26.860 --> 00:29.350
You do get you quit
the wizard competition, right?

00:29.390 --> 00:31.450
Pretty soon you're gonna
lose all your powers.

00:31.490 --> 00:32.689
You need to learn how to survive

00:32.729 --> 00:34.460
without using magic for everything you do.

00:34.490 --> 00:36.130
Harper, that's ridiculous.

00:36.160 --> 00:38.300
I don't use magic for everything that I do.

00:38.370 --> 00:39.800
Oh, really?

00:39.840 --> 00:42.370
Do you even know how to zip up
that sweatshirt on your own?

00:42.410 --> 00:44.970
Yes.

00:51.150 --> 00:54.250
There, see?

00:54.280 --> 00:57.490
That is the saddest thing I have ever seen.

00:57.520 --> 01:00.720
Alex, I am serious.
What are you gonna do

01:00.760 --> 01:03.520
when you can't flash in and out of places?

01:03.560 --> 01:05.090
You need to learn how to drive.

01:05.129 --> 01:08.130
Right. Well, let's go
to Driver's Ed.

01:08.160 --> 01:10.760
Yay! I can't wait
to get my license.

01:10.800 --> 01:13.470
Then I can communicate with my
fellow New York City drivers.

01:13.500 --> 01:15.330
"Hey, jerk!
You cut me off!

01:15.370 --> 01:18.100
Pull over, I'm gonna
take you down!"

